      "text": "菜鸟上门请多关照",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 157.81,
      "time_str": "02:37.810",
      "text": "于明日成为你的骄傲（粤）",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 162.22,
      "time_str": "02:42.220",
      "text": "我要努力向前奔跑",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 166.66,
      "time_str": "02:46.660",
      "text": "来日定会飞的更高（粵）",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 171.23,
      "time_str": "02:51.230",
      "text": "菜鸟在追 它飞呀飞（粵）",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 175.88,
      "time_str": "02:55.880",
      "text": "轻柔的晚风 它吹呀吹（粵）",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 180.53,
      "time_str": "03:00.530",
      "text": "若有泪痕 将它拂去（粵）",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 184.84,
      "time_str": "03:04.840",
      "text": "热爱的人 把梦留低（粵）",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 189.67,
      "time_str": "03:09.670",
      "text": "菜鸟在追 它飞呀飞（粵）",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 193.71,
